<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="External_links">External links</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Motion_perception&amp;action=edit&amp;section=22" title="Edit section: External links">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<ul><li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://archive.is/20121210193604/http://neurovision.berkeley.edu/Demonstrations/matthew/reichardt.html">Interactive Reichardt Detector</a></li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tGJYSIBETho">Video demonstrating second-order motion perception</a></li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.siliconmentor.com/visual-motion-analysis/">Visual Motion Analysis</a></li></ul>
<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Labs_specialising_in_motion_research">Labs specialising in motion research</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Motion_perception&amp;action=edit&amp;section=23" title="Edit section: Labs specialising in motion research">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
<ul><li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.psychology.nottingham.ac.uk/research/vision/">Visual Neuroscience</a>, <a href="/wiki/University_of_Nottingham" title="University of Nottingham">University of Nottingham</a></li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.mvr.mcgill.ca/home.html">McGill Vision Research</a>, <a href="/wiki/McGill_University" title="McGill University">McGill University</a></li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://archive.is/20130112060439/http://www.purveslab.net/main">Purves Lab</a>, <a href="/wiki/Duke_University" title="Duke University">Duke University</a></li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://cvr.yorku.ca/home/">Center for Vision Research</a>, <a href="/wiki/York_University" title="York University">York University</a></li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://ilab.usc.edu/">iLab</a>, <a href="/wiki/University_of_Southern_California" title="University of Southern California">University of Southern California</a></li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20121102224952/http://www.cin.uni-tuebingen.de/research/bartels.php">Vision and Cognition</a>, <a href="/wiki/University_of_T%C3%BCbingen" title="University of Tübingen">University of Tübingen</a></li></ul>
